  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868110/extras/5cff5bee9df5d34a9e19c4e602d02851.avif?t=1756401458\" width=618 height=132 /></span><br><br>Welcome to Street of the Cats, an object game that involves searching for hidden cats in the neighborhood.<br><br>Find all the cats by clicking on them, in a hand-drawn background.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868110/extras/8b214ce37974b5a680711a45d4a8c6a9.avif?t=1756401458\" width=618 height=66 /></span><br><br>    😻 Over 300 cats<br>    🎨 05 Scenarios<br>    💡 Hint system for cat location<br>    🔎 Zoom<br>    🌗 Contrast settings<br>    🎵 Relaxing music<br>    😺Meows<br>    🔉 Sound control<br>    💾 Save and load system<br>    🎮 Steam achievements",
